Mengniu Shares Slide in Hong Kong After FT Report on Pfizer Bid

-- B y   M a r c o   L u i
-- 
2011-10-24T02:06:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-24/mengniu-shares-slide-in-hong-kong-after-ft-report-on-pfizer-bid.html
China Mengniu Dairy Co. fell in Hong
Kong trading after the Financial Times reported that the company
is in discussions with UBS AG over a potential bid for  Pfizer
Inc. (PFE) ’s infant nutrition business.  The stock dropped 5.2 percent to HK$24.85 as of 10:02 a.m.
on the city’s stock exchange.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Marco Lui at 
 mlui11@bloomberg.net  